data.description: Hardwood floors, fenced-in yard, and a full daylight basement stubbed for a bathroom are ready for your finishing touches. Homes don't come available in Glen Laurel often but now you own this executive home with over 6,000 square ft including the basement. High ceilings, two separate living areas, an open kitchen with plenty of counter space overlooking the deck and fenced-in private yard. This home is perfect for entertaining and future basement expansion to your desire. You could add more bedrooms, or entertainment space like a game room or movie theatre. The spacious owners' suite overlooks the backyard and features a large double vanity and separate jetted tub and shower. You will not believe the size of the walk-in closet. If you've always wanted space to put a sitting bench or island in your closet, this is the home for you! Too many benefits to add here. This home is a must see!!
